    <item>
      <title>中美贸易战爆发 铜价缩减涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/copper-and-zinc-climb-as-trump-delays-tariffs-on-canada-mexico</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受全球贸易紧张局势大幅升级影响，铜价缩减涨幅，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对中国商品征收 10% 的关税，而北京方面则出台了一系列措施予以回应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/copper-and-zinc-climb-as-trump-delays-tariffs-on-canada-mexico</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 01:25:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普发起中美贸易战 黄金价格稳定在历史高位附近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/gold-holds-near-record-high-as-tariff-confusion-aids-haven-bids</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对中国征收 10% 的关税后，金价稳定在历史高位附近，提振了避险需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-04/gold-holds-near-record-high-as-tariff-confusion-aids-haven-bids</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Feb 2025 00:15:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国对美国关税采取报复措施后，油价延续跌势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-february-4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国对美国出口的部分商品征收关税之后，油价延续下跌趋势，这为世界两大经济体之间爆发新一轮贸易战埋下了伏笔，威胁到全球经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-february-4</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 23:35:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价暴跌，美国期货因中国关税而下滑：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国对美国新一轮关税采取报复性措施后，股指期货下跌，油价暴跌，标志着世界两大经济体之间贸易战重启。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 22:34:23 GMT</pubDate>
